@sandbergja and I deployed to staging and did a QA on the UI. 

1. Search results is missing 'You searched for:'
2.   'Quick Links' are missing https://github.com/pulibrary/DSS/pull/329
3.  Modal close button is not visible. This is an existing issue in production. The difference is: In production a user can close the modal when clicking outside of the modal or using the escape button. In the blacklight 8 PR only escape works. resolved by https://github.com/pulibrary/DSS/pull/330

@kevinreiss which of the above issues needs to be fixed in order to merge this PR? From our perspective 2 and 3 should be fixed as part of this PR.
